ASSEMBLING:

          1.   Modify or use the Z3BASE.LIB appropriate for your
               system.

          2.   Using M80 and L80 assembler and linker as follows:

                    m80 =zap
                    l80 zap,zap/e/n
                    n
                    erase zap.rel
                    rename zap.rcp=zap.com
                    ldr zap.rcp
          
           3.   As with most RCPs H will display the table of 
                commands available.

